8) $\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\ln (n!)}{n \ln n}=\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\ln 1+\ln 2+\cdots+\ln n}{n \ln n}$
$$\begin{aligned}
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n \ln n} \sum_{k=1}^{n} \ln k \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n \ln n} \sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\ln \frac{k}{n}+\ln n\right) \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n \ln n}\left[\sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\ln \frac{k}{n}\right)+\sum_{k=1}^{n} \ln n\right] \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n \ln n}\left[\sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\ln \frac{k}{n}\right)+n \ln n\right] \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n \ln n} \sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\ln \frac{k}{n}\right)+1 \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{\ln n} \sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\ln \frac{k}{n}\right) \frac{1}{n}+1
\end{aligned}$$
$$\begin{aligned}
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{\ln n} \int_{0}^{1} \ln x d x+1 \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{-1}{\ln n}+1=1
\end{aligned}$$
